<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/jul/24/">&#x27a0;</a> July 24, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="motherload" >

        
        <a name="002743"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.miniclip.com/games/motherload/en/">MotherLoad</a></h4>

        

        <p>A splendidly fun flashgame, drilling down for minerals, and returning to the surface before you run out of fuel, whilst cashing in the minerals and upgrading your driller.  I could see me getting quite addicted to this!</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
